<p>Hi,</p>

<p>
  <strong><%= @inviter.full_name %></strong> (<%= @inviter.email %>) has invited you to collaborate on
  the incident <strong><%= @incident.display_incident_name %></strong> in Action Plan.
</p>

<p>Click the button below to set your password and finish creating your account:</p>

<p>
  <%= link_to "Accept invitation", @accept_url, style: "display:inline-block;padding:10px 18px;background:#0052cc;color:#fff;text-decoration:none;border-radius:4px;" %>
</p>

<p>Or copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
<p><%= @accept_url %></p>

<p style="color:#666;font-size:12px;">
  If you don't recognize this invitation, you can safely ignore this email.
</p>
